---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import myOfficeImage from '../assets/images/2026/02/my-office.jpg';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn more about Daniel Deepak.">
  <div class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-12">About Me</h1>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[360px_1fr] gap-8 md:gap-12 mb-12">
      <div>
        <Image
          src={myOfficeImage}
          alt="Daniel’s office workspace"
          width={360}
          class="rounded-lg h-auto"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="prose space-y-6">
        <p>
          Hello, I’m Daniel. I come from a humble background. I grew up admiring people who did things better than me. I made myself better by following their footprints and I still do. Along the way I inspire others to grow.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">My Philosophy</h2>

        <p>
          I started questioning things from my young age. People around me think I’m one of a kind. But I’m not. The philosophy of Stoicism will explain why.
        </p>

        <div class="aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
          <iframe
            width="100%"
            height="100%"
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/R9OCA6UFE-0"
            title="YouTube video player"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
            allowfullscreen>
          </iframe>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">My Work</h2>

        <p>
          I’m a developer at Elegant Themes. Our customers use Divi, our flagship product, to build their business websites and blogs and make money without the need to write even a single line of code. I suggest you to give Divi a try.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  :global(.prose) {
    color: #333;
  }

  :global(.prose a) {
    color: #2563eb;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  :global(.prose a:hover) {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  :global(.prose h2) {
    color: #0a0a0a;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  :global(.prose ul) {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  :global(.prose li) {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  :global(.prose strong) {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  :global(.prose p) {
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
</style>
